        {
          "id": "ba854d9afaf6_5",
          "href": null,
          "name": "e9ae",
          "text": "To embark on a pilgrimage is also a very ancient way of mirroring the individual’s spiritual journey of awakening and transformation of consciousness in a physical journey of walking towards a meaningful destination or sacred site.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [
            {
