        {
          "id": "ba854d9afaf6_8",
          "href": null,
          "name": "d59d",
          "text": "The pilgrimage to Mecca, the Hajj is one of the commitments that every Muslim vows to complete at least one in his life. The Kumbh Mela is the largest recorded gathering of human beings on the planet and one of the most important pilgrimages for Hindus. The pilgrimage route that encircles Mount Kailash, a sacred site shared by Hindus, Buddhists, Jains, honours the life giving qualities of the Indus river at the foothills of this holy mountain. Mount Kailash has never been climbed, out of respect!",
          "metadata": null,
