        {
          "id": "ba854d9afaf6_15",
          "href": null,
          "name": "9912",
          "text": "Sabine Lichtenfels is a co-founder of Tamera ecovillage in Portugal, deeply dedicated to creating peace on earth, peace in all human relationships, peace between the sexes, and (as one particular focus) peace between Israel and Palestine. In her autobiographical book GRACE — Pilgrimage for a Future without War Sabine tells the story her own commitment to becoming a pilgrim for peace on Earth and recounts a number of pilgrimage journeys she has undertaken since. Below is a copy of Sabine Lichtenfels’ personal prayer for peace.",
