          "id": "ba854d9afaf6_17",
          "href": null,
          "name": "5424",
          "text": "Where there was pain, let healing awaken. Where there was anger, let the power for change emerge. Where there was fear, let safety and trust grow. Where there were enemies, let the awakening of mutual compassion begin. Where there was oppression, let freedom reign. Where nations were divided, let sympathy for planet earth lead to shared responsibility.",
