          "type": "PQ"
        },
        {
          "id": "ba854d9afaf6_18",
          "href": null,
          "name": "17a7",
          "text": "We have come as a reminder: If we want planet earth to survive then all the walls of separation must fall -the walls between peoples, between Israel and Palestine, between Europe and Africa, between the so-called first and third world. And likewise with the walls that we have erected in our own psyches, the walls between the genders, and the walls between humans and all creatures.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [
            {
              "end": 383,
              "href": null,
              "rel": null,
              "start": 0,
              "title": null,
              "anchorType": null,
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "EM",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            }
          ],
          "type": "PQ"
        },
        {
          "id": "ba854d9afaf6_19",
          "href": null,
          "name": "517c",
          "text": "We have come as a reminder of the original beauty and truth of life: Every living being has a right to be free and to unfold, a right to love, and a right to genuine truth and to trust.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [
            {
              "end": 185,
              "href": null,
              "rel": null,
              "start": 0,
              "title": null,
              "anchorType": null,
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "EM",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            }
          ],
          "type": "PQ"
        },
        {
          "id": "ba854d9afaf6_20",
          "href": null,
          "name": "88c3",
          "text": "Let us set examples for overcoming violence wherever we are. Let us stand up for life and for love so that fear can vanish on earth. Let us form a worldwide circle of power to safeguard all creation. May this prayer or something better come to be. Thank you and Amen.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [
            {
              "end": 267,
              "href": null,
              "rel": null,
              "start": 0,
              "title": null,
              "anchorType": null,
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "EM",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            }
          ],
          "type": "PQ"
        },
        {
          "id": "ba854d9afaf6_21",
          "href": null,
          "name": "a786",
          "text": "Sabine Lichtenfels’s pilgrimage journeys were inspired by the life of Mildred Norman Ryder who at the age of 44 called herself Peace Pilgrim and spent the last 28 years of her life walking over 25000 miles for peace.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [
