        {
          "id": "ba854d9afaf6_22",
          "href": null,
          "name": "2074",
          "text": "Sabine Lichtenfels is engaged in international peace work with a focus on the Middle East and has led several peace pilgrimages through Israel and the West Bank (2005, 2007) and through Colombia (2008). Here is a short video (6mins) of Sabine speaking about creating peace during the Grace pilgrimage. (image left; image right)",
